Result: A and B grains are not significantly different (p < 0.9). C grains are significantly different (p > 0.99)
```{r, echo=FALSE}
#Ft
kable(pvalue_ft_gem %>% 
        rename(`p-value` = pvalue) %>% 
        unite("GEM Compare", var1:var2, sep = " vs. ") %>% 
        relocate(`GEM Compare`, .before = `p-value`))


